Advanced V6 Actual Screenshot Ready Lead Edition</h1>
<p><strong>Target role:</strong> Internal lead-level Python + AWS position<br />
<strong>Candidate positioning:</strong> 4 years total experience, with hands-on exposure to Python, AWS Lambda, 
S3, Textract, SQS/SNS, Step Functions, Glue, EC2/FSx, FastAPI/Flask, production deployments, troubleshooting, 
documentation, and stakeholder coordination.<br />
<strong>Goal:</strong> Prepare like a 6-year engineer by focusing not only on service names, but on how systems 
behave under load, failure, cost pressure, security constraints, and operational incidents.</p>
