<h3 id="retry-decorator">Retry decorator</h3>

## Page 25

<pre><code class="language-python">import time
import functools
def retry(max_attempts=3, delay=1, allowed_exceptions=(Exception,)):
 def outer(func):
 @functools.wraps(func)
 def inner(*args, **kwargs):
 last_error = None
 for attempt in range(1, max_attempts + 1):
 try:
 return func(*args, **kwargs)
 except allowed_exceptions as exc:
 last_error = exc
 if attempt == max_attempts:
 raise
 time.sleep(delay)
 raise last_error
 return inner
 return outer
</code></pre>
<p>Important: for AWS SDK calls, prefer <strong>SDK retry configuration</strong> plus application-level 
idempotency instead of blindly retrying everything.</p>
