<h3 id="synchronous-api-gateway-lambda">Synchronous API Gateway Lambda</h3>
<pre><code class="language-text">Client -&gt; API Gateway -&gt; Lambda -&gt; response
</code></pre>
<p>Good for:</p>

## Page 59

<ul>
<li>Simple APIs</li>
<li>Lightweight backend services</li>
<li>Internal tools</li>
</ul>
<p>Bad for:</p>
<ul>
<li>Long-running jobs</li>
<li>Heavy PDF processing</li>
<li>Multi-step workflows</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="async-pattern-for-long-jobs">Async pattern for long jobs</h3>
<pre><code class="language-text">Client uploads file
API creates job record
API sends message to queue
Worker processes job
Frontend polls /jobs/{id}
</code></pre>
