<h3 id="partial-batch-failure-response">Partial batch failure response</h3>
<p>If processing one message fails in a batch, you do not want successful messages retried unnecessarily.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">
def lambda_handler(event, context):
 failures = []
 for record in event[&quot;Records&quot;]:
 try:
 process_message(record)
 except Exception:
 failures.append({&quot;itemIdentifier&quot;: record[&quot;messageId&quot;]})
 return {&quot;batchItemFailures&quot;: failures}
</code></pre>
