<li>Use SSM Session Manager instead of SSH where possible.</li>
<li>Install CloudWatch agent for logs/metrics.</li>
<li>Use Auto Scaling Group for HA.</li>
<li>Use AMI/user-data/IaC for repeatable provisioning.</li>
<li>Patch regularly.</li>
