Validator -&gt; SQS message {job_id,bucket,key}
SQS -&gt; Worker Lambda
Worker -&gt; Textract / parser
Worker -&gt; save result to S3 processed/
Worker -&gt; update DB: COMPLETED or FAILED
Frontend -&gt; GET /jobs/{job_id}
Optional -&gt; WebSocket/SNS/email notification
</code></pre>
