<p>Lead answer:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;I use FIFO only when ordering is a real requirement. Otherwise Standard queue gives better throughput 
and simpler scaling. For FIFO, I choose message group ID carefully because one hot group can bottleneck 
processing.&quot;</p>
