<h2 id="62-case-study-2-webhook-ingestion-at-scale">62. Case Study 2: Webhook ingestion at scale</h2>
<p>Requirement:</p>
<pre><code class="language-text">Receive payment/telephony/messaging webhooks reliably.
</code></pre>
<p>Architecture:</p>
<pre><code class="language-text">Webhook provider
 -&gt; API Gateway/Lambda or ALB/FastAPI
 -&gt; verify signature
 -&gt; store raw webhook event

