- use schema evolution strategy
- compact small files
- lifecycle raw old data
</code></pre>
<p>Failure handling:</p>
<pre><code class="language-text">- failed job alarm
- bad records to quarantine prefix
- rerun by partition/date
- job bookmark reset only deliberately
