aws lambda delete-function-concurrency \
 --function-name invoice-worker</code></pre>
<p><strong>Interview answer:</strong> "I use reserved concurrency when I want to cap a Lambda so it does not 
overwhelm a downstream system. For SQS triggers, I may also set maximum concurrency on the event source mapping 
to control one queue independently."</p>
