 assert result[&quot;invoice_no&quot;] == &quot;INV-1&quot;
 repository.save.assert_called_once()
</code></pre>
<p>Lead answer:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;I isolate pure business logic from AWS integration code. Then I unit test core logic with mocks and 
integration-test AWS paths separately using dev resources or local emulators where appropriate.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
