<h2 id="30-rdsaurora-for-python-engineers">30. RDS/Aurora for Python engineers</h2>
<p>RDS manages relational databases like PostgreSQL/MySQL.</p>
<p>Use RDS/Aurora when:</p>
<ul>
<li>Strong relational model</li>
<li>SQL joins</li>
<li>transactions</li>
<li>constraints</li>
<li>reporting</li>
<li>consistent schema</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="python-connection-example">Python connection example</h3>
<pre><code class="language-python">import psycopg
