<h2 id="51-paginators">51. Paginators</h2>
<p>Many AWS APIs return paginated results.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">paginator = s3.get_paginator(&quot;list_objects_v2&quot;)
for page in paginator.paginate(Bucket=&quot;my-bucket&quot;, Prefix=&quot;raw/&quot;):
 for obj in page.get(&quot;Contents&quot;, []):
 print(obj[&quot;Key&quot;])
</code></pre>
<p>Never assume one <code>list_objects_v2</code> call returns all objects.</p>
