<h2 id="52-waiters">52. Waiters</h2>
<p>Waiters poll until a resource reaches a desired state.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">ec2 = boto3.client(&quot;ec2&quot;)
waiter = ec2.get_waiter(&quot;instance_running&quot;)
waiter.wait(InstanceIds=[&quot;i-1234567890abcdef0&quot;])
</code></pre>
<p>Use waiters instead of manual sleep loops when available.</p>
