<h2 id="53-idempotent-worker-pattern">53. Idempotent worker pattern</h2>
<pre><code class="language-python">def process_job(job_id):
 job = repository.get(job_id)
 if job.status == &quot;COMPLETED&quot;:
 return job.result
 repository.mark_processing(job_id)
 try:
 result = external_processing(job)
 repository.mark_completed(job_id, result)
 return result
 except Exception as exc:
 repository.mark_failed(job_id, str(exc))
 raise
</code></pre>
<p>Idempotency keys can be:</p>
<ul>
<li>job ID</li>
<li>S3 bucket + key + version ID</li>
<li>external request ID</li>
<li>event ID</li>
<li>hash of payload</li>
</ul>
