<p>Lead answer:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;I reuse stateless expensive objects like boto3 clients and DB connection pools carefully, but I avoid 
storing request-specific mutable data globally because Lambda containers can be reused.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
