<h2 id="25-dlq-and-poison-messages">25. DLQ and poison messages</h2>
<p>A poison message is a message that repeatedly fails due to invalid data or a non-transient bug.</p>
<h3 id="dlq-flow">DLQ flow</h3>
<pre><code class="language-text">SQS main queue
 -&gt; message fails

