<h2 id="55-playbook-cost-spike">55. Playbook: Cost spike</h2>
<p>Check:</p>
<pre><code class="language-text">- CloudWatch usage metrics
- Cost Explorer by service/tag
- Lambda invocations/duration
- NAT Gateway data processing
- S3 requests/storage classes
- Glue DPU hours
- CloudWatch logs ingestion
- cross-region data transfer
</code></pre>
<p>Common causes:</p>
<pre><code class="language-text">- recursive Lambda trigger
- infinite retry loop

## Page 303

- verbose debug logs
- unbounded Glue job
- NAT used for AWS service traffic instead of VPC endpoint
- keeping temporary files forever
</code></pre>
<p>Lead answer:</p>
