<h2 id="63-case-study-3-data-lake-etl-pipeline">63. Case Study 3: Data lake ETL pipeline</h2>
<p>Requirement:</p>
<pre><code class="language-text">Daily raw data lands in S3. Transform and expose analytics through Athena/BI.
</code></pre>
<p>Architecture:</p>
<pre><code class="language-text">S3 raw zone
 -&gt; Glue crawler/Data Catalog
 -&gt; Glue ETL job converts CSV/JSON to Parquet
 -&gt; S3 curated zone partitioned by date/source
 -&gt; Athena queries curated tables
 -&gt; QuickSight/BI/reporting
