 -&gt; inventory service reserves stock
 -&gt; notification service sends message

## Page 308

-&gt; order status updated through events
</code></pre>
<p>Important concepts:</p>
<pre><code class="language-text">- saga pattern
- eventual consistency
- compensating actions
- idempotent event handling
- correlation ID
- outbox pattern
</code></pre>
<p>Outbox table:</p>
