<h2 id="71-nat-gateway-hidden-cost">71. NAT Gateway hidden cost</h2>
<p>NAT Gateway can become expensive when private subnets send large traffic through it.</p>
<p>Mitigation:</p>
<pre><code class="language-text">- use S3 Gateway Endpoint
