How debounce works
Suppose user types:
r
re
rea
react
Without debounce, filter runs 4 times.
With debounce:
user types r → timer starts
user types re before 500ms → old timer cleared
user types rea before 500ms → old timer cleared
user stops at react
after 500ms → filter runs only once
This line clears the old timer:

